summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Eastlake Avenue from Almy Street to Twelfth Avenue North in the City of Seattle, by grading, regrading, curbing and gutting under Ordinance No. 15063, creating Local Improvement District No. 1365 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
